A beautiful example of Swiss Green Opal, this marquise cut loose gemstone at first glance seems opaque, but when seen in the sunlight, it gives off an amazing lustrous sheen.  This loose gemstone would make a stunning centre stone for a bangle or statement ring, or equally a pendant. Swiss Green Opal is considered to have healing properties for the mind and body as well as helping to sharpen the memory of the wearer.
